text: avei kadaoy del a l laoh bratan aoy mnoussa lok nouv kdei me tda krounea( dauchchea phdal tukaphlieng leaphosakkar sokhpheap chamnehdoeng)ku kmean anaknea mneak ach reareang vea laey . haey avei del trong reareang ku kmean anaknea mneak ach banhchoun vea banteabpi trong laey . haey trong mha khlangpouke mha ktebandet
